# Back-Pain

Back Pain - PH406

## Requirements

[Docker](https://docs.docker.com/install/) and [CWLTool](https://github.com/common-workflow-language/cwltool#install)

## Configuration

Specify input dataset path in [Back-Pain-inputs.yml](Back-Pain-inputs.yml).

## Usage

Run: `cwltool Back-Pain.cwl Back-Pain-inputs.yml`
